'''威斯特布路浸信會'''（Westboro Baptist Church），[[美國|美國]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]]的一個[[宗教團體|宗教團體]]，由[[弗雷德·菲尔普斯|弗雷德·菲尔普斯]]創立，成員大部份是創立者菲尔普斯的親人，是一家族教會。威斯特布路浸信會沒有與美國任何浸信會組織有聯繫。

威斯特布路浸信會有一個叫「上帝恨同性戀（God hate fags，fag是[[歧視語|歧視語]]，解釋為[[男同性戀|男同性戀]]）[http://www.godhatesfags.com/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.godhatesfags.com/ |date=20210307223124 }}」的網站，專門引用《[[聖經|聖經]]》內容，譴責[[同性戀|同性戀]]、[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]、[[變性|變性]]。

威斯特布路浸信会是一个以极端反[[同性恋|同性恋]]立场和游行示威活动而为人所知的[[独立教会|独立教会]]。<ref>[http://www.godhatesfags.com/ "God Hates Fags"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.godhatesfags.com/ |date=20210307223124 }}, Westboro Baptist Church. Retrieved June 20,2010.</ref> 该教会游行示威的方式包括纠察美国军人葬礼和亵渎美国国旗。<ref>[http://www.timesunion.com/default/article/School-plans-safe-show-554814.php "School Plans Safe Show"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesunion.com/default/article/School-plans-safe-show-554814.php |date=20210225192911 }},Times Union(Albany,NY). Retrieved July 1,2011.</ref> 这个教会被广泛地称作为宣扬仇恨的组织并且受到反诽谤联盟和南方贫困法律中心的监视。<ref>[http://www.adl.org/learn/ext_us/WBC/default.asp?LEARN_Cat=Extremism&LEARN_SubCat=Extremism_in_America&xpicked=3&item=WBC "Westboro Baptist Church"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.adl.org/learn/ext_us/WBC/default.asp?LEARN_Cat=Extremism&LEARN_SubCat=Extremism_in_America&xpicked=3&item=WBC |date=20100707223315 }}, Anti-Defamation League. Retrieved June 20,2010.</ref><ref>[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Westboro_Baptist_Church "HateMap KS"] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Westboro_Baptist_Church |date=20210228222730 }}, Southern Poverty Law Center. Retrieved June 20,2010.</ref> 该教会由领导者弗莱德·菲尔普斯以及基本来自他家庭的教徒组成。<ref name="John Blake(March 14,2010).">[http://edition.cnn.com/2010/US/05/05/hate.preacher/index.html?hpt=C2 "Most-hated, anti-gay preacher once fought for civil rights"] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/US/05/05/hate.preacher/index.html?hpt=C2 |date=20210224053525 }}, CNN. Retrieved May 20,2010.</ref> 2011年威斯特布路浸信会宣布它拥有40名信徒。<ref>[http://blogs.sparenot.com/workmen/2011/10/27/you-are-still-alive-now-is-the-time-to-repent/ "You Are Still Alive:NOW Is The Time To Repent"] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.sparenot.com/workmen/2011/10/27/you-are-still-alive-now-is-the-time-to-repent/ |date=20120110104729 }}, Westboro Baptist Church. October 27,2011. Retrieved November 11,2011.</ref>这个教会的总部位于堪萨斯州议会大厦往西3公里的一个住宅小区内。具体地址是美国堪萨斯州托皮卡市3701西12号大街。

威斯特布路浸信会不与任何已知的浸信会大会或组织有联系，尽管主流浸信会反对该教会和它的领导者，威斯特布路浸信会声称自己遵循原初[[浸信宗|浸信宗]][[教义|教义]]與原始的[[克尔文主义|克尔文主义]]信条。<ref>[http://www.godhatesfags.com/wbcinfo/aboutwbc.html "About Westboro Baptist Church"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.godhatesfags.com/wbcinfo/aboutwbc.html |date=20170618001055 }}, God Hates Fags. Westboro Baptist Church. Retrieved October 14,2010.</ref><ref>Montgomery David(September 9,2008)[http://primitivebaptist.info/mambo//index2.php?option=com_content&do_pdf=1&id=1434 "Disclaimer"] {{Wayback|url=http://primitivebaptist.info/mambo//index2.php?option=com_content&do_pdf=1&id=1434 |date=20181001120841 }}, Primitive Baptist Online</ref>

