报复。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kake.com/news/headlines/2206092.html|title=Controlling Funeral Protests?|publisher=KAKE|location=Wichita, KS|date=January 16, 2006|accessdate=August 30, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060421074618/http://www.kake.com/news/headlines/2206092.html|archivedate=2006年4月21日}}</ref>

