=== 各种恶搞 ===
常用的反威斯特布路标语是“上帝恨无花果”。反威斯特布路的标语来源于圣经中一节关于[[上帝|上帝]]和他对[[无花果|无花果]]感受的经文，通过改一个字母加将英文单词“同性恋”（Fag）变成“[[无花果|无花果]]”（Fig）来恶搞威斯特布路的经典示威游行标语“上帝恨同性恋”。“上帝恨无花果”出现在芝加哥大学反对游行上，同时出现在斯帕坦堡，南卡罗来纳，朴茨茅斯和新汉普郡。<ref>Christman, Zach(March 13,2009).[http://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/Students-Counter-Protest-Westboro-Baptist-Church-at-University-of-Chicago-UIC-God-Hates-Figs-and-Shrimp.html "God Hates Figs(and Shrimp)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/Students-Counter-Protest-Westboro-Baptist-Church-at-University-of-Chicago-UIC-God-Hates-Figs-and-Shrimp.html |date=20190125184629 }}, NBC Chicago. Retrieved March 3,2011</ref><ref>[http://www.goupstate.com/article/20110215/ARTICLES/102151024/1088/sports?Title=Kansas-church-a-no-show-at-Converse-but-film-draws-a-crowd "Westboro Baptist Church of Topeka, Kan, a no-show at Converse"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.goupstate.com/article/20110215/ARTICLES/102151024/1088/sports?Title=Kansas-church-a-no-show-at-Converse-but-film-draws-a-crowd |date=20160426163514 }}, Goupstate.com. February 15,2011. Retrieved March 3,2011.</ref><ref>Jeanne McCartin. [http://www.seacoastonline.com/articles/20110224-NEWS-102240415 "Hundreds speak out against hate in city"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seacoastonline.com/articles/20110224-NEWS-102240415 |date=20140519185453 }}, SeacoastOnline.com. Retrieved March 3,2011</ref> 非威斯特布路组织恢复理智协会也用过这个标语。<ref>Kent Hayden(November 7,2010). [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/kent-hayden-mdiv/the-religion-of-a-satiric_b_777097.html "The Religion of a satirical Generation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/kent-hayden-mdiv/the-religion-of-a-satiric_b_777097.html |date=20160303182345 }}, The Huffington Post. Retrieved March 3,2011.</ref> 使用这个标语已经成为美国公民联合会和其他人保持理智的象征。<ref>[http://www.aclu.org/blog/free-speech-lgbt-rights/god-hates-figs "God Hates Figs"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aclu.org/blog/free-speech-lgbt-rights/god-hates-figs |date=20141129131846 }}, American Civil Liberties Union. Retrieved March 3,2011.</ref>

在反游行上分发的文件引用了圣经的章节，说耶稣认为任何人都不应吃无花果，并且让一棵无花果树枯萎了，还保证说，作为惩罚会让让一个人变得像坏掉的无花果。<ref>Savage,Dan(March 12,2009) [http://slog.thestranger.com/slog/archives/2009/03/12/god_hates_figs "God Hates Figs"] {{Wayback|url=http://slog.thestranger.com/slog/archives/2009/03/12/god_hates_figs |date=20160314063334 }}, The Stranger(Seattle). Retrieved March 3,2011.</ref> 这些都是真实的语段，但并不是圣经里对无花果的所有描述。其他的组织也恶搞过威斯特布路浸信会的标语，包括“上帝恨弗莱德·菲尔普斯”、“上帝恨包包”和“上帝恨鲜虾”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.godhatesfredphelps.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-05-13 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211161615/http://www.godhatesfredphelps.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://godhatesbags.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-05-13 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111214859/http://godhatesbags.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.godhatesshrimp.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-05-13 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216203217/http://www.godhatesshrimp.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

